lass=\"hkgmoji\" />：Hi,你有冇見到樓主？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩，唔撚係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青山肯收你咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :，唔好同人講，我&hellip;坑渠偷走入黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩屌你老母，你個垃圾都夠膽話自己係精神病人，你係垃圾唔係人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁...咁我真係人吖嘛，我&hellip;我會俾心機食屎㗎<br />\n<br />\n我聽到即刻火都嚟埋<br />\n一嘢喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你同我跪喺度！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢俾我嘅氣勢嚇到一嘢跪咗喺度，眼角仲開始濕濕地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母偷入青山都算，仲要去做食屎狗？咁劉馬車都可以做律師啦屌你老母！有心，我夠有心做國家主席吖，你俾我做吖不如！？你連教人入青山都分分鐘唔夠料吖<br />\n你都係返鄉下執牛屎把啦<br />\n<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我先停，放佢一馬<br />\n反正啲90後都屌唔醒㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：層主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：層主好型"},{"pid":"f241bd32761bb031de83672a901ddd18d2946d0d","tid":2005791,"uid":311034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"30分穩入 I 大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前途無可限量"}]}